divs: Sighting DetailsArrived at hunting camp. Got out of truck, looked up in north sky. My girlfriend and I noticed two UFO'S spiraling, leaving a comet like tail with a hook shaped that followed the objects. I snapped one pic with my digital camera, then put it on video mode. The second object appeared shortly after the first. Objects headed east toward Lake Huron, then faded out.
Summary: Observed Two Spiraling UFO'S with comet like tails
